channel.title: Why cant i join superman20.servegame.com?!
channel.description:
I followed the "Creating a Private Server" tutorial and it didnt help! I run moparscape and the Project16V45 run.bat, And i try to log on to superman20.servegame.com and it says that that server dosent exist... then i try to log on to 127.0.0.1 and the project16 application says that a user is joining...
Why can i join locally but not on superman20.servegame.com??
Thanks, mrgibblet

item.title: Why cant i join superman20.servegame.com?!
item.dc:creator: @brownieman brownieman
item.description:
@brownieman wrote:

have u followed all the steps http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,643.0.html is good

Fixing "Can Not Find Specified Location" and "Device is not ready" Right click on Run&Compile and click edit delete all the code in it and replace with this:

Code:
@echo off
COLOR 08
title YOURSERVERNAME Client
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin\java.exe” server
pause
or if that one doesnt work try this one

Code:
@echo off
COLOR 08
title YOURSERVERNAME Client
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\java.exe” server
pause

That sums this tutorial up. Thanks for reading.
